# Normalise everything to LF in the repository and in the working tree.
#
# This project is developed on Windows but built on a Raspberry Pi, which
# clones this repo directly. A CRLF checkout breaks shell scripts there with
# an opaque "bad interpreter: No such file or directory" — scripts/setup-pi.sh
# is the one that bites, and docs/raspberry-pi.md documents the symptom.
# Forcing LF removes the failure mode instead of documenting a workaround.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Binary assets: never touch these.
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.ico binary
*.icns binary
*.woff binary
*.woff2 binary
*.deb binary
*.exe binary
